name: Slaunch
description: Slaunch is the first launchpad powered by Initial Attention Offering (IAO), built natively on the Sui Network. It introduces a new launch primitive where early-stage projects can raise capital through community attention and participation. Unlike traditional IDOs, Slaunch rewards users for both attention and commitment. Through its dual system - Mindshare and Points - users gain access to launches by contributing on social platforms and participating on-chain with the $S token (hold, stake, trade). No VCs. No team allocation. 100% fairlaunch. Slaunch turns participation into power.
